@startuml 功能模块图
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

title EduSphere 在线教育平台 - 功能模块图

package "用户管理模块" as UserModule {
  [用户注册] as Register
  [用户登录] as Login
  [个人信息管理] as Profile
  [密码修改] as PasswordChange
  [头像上传] as AvatarUpload
  [角色权限控制] as RoleControl
}

package "课程管理模块" as CourseModule {
  [课程浏览] as CourseBrowse
  [课程搜索] as CourseSearch
  [课程详情] as CourseDetail
  [课程分类] as CourseCategory
  [课程评价] as CourseReview
  [课程大纲] as CourseOutline
  [课程状态管理] as CourseStatus
}

package "教师创作模块" as TeacherModule {
  [教师工作台] as TeacherDashboard
  [课程创建] as CourseCreate
  [课程编辑] as CourseEdit
  [章节管理] as SectionManage
  [课时管理] as LessonManage
  [课程发布] as CoursePublish
  [课程统计] as CourseStats
}

package "学习模块" as LearningModule {
  [学习页面] as LearningPage
  [视频播放] as VideoPlayer
  [文档查看] as DocumentView
  [测验功能] as QuizSystem
  [学习进度] as LearningProgress
  [学习记录] as LearningRecord
}

package "购买模块" as PurchaseModule {
  [课程购买] as CoursePurchase
  [余额充值] as BalanceRecharge
  [购买记录] as PurchaseRecord
  [我的课程] as MyCourses
  [支付处理] as PaymentProcess
}

package "管理模块" as AdminModule {
  [管理员后台] as AdminDashboard
  [课程审核] as CourseReview
  [用户管理] as UserManage
  [数据统计] as DataStatistics
  [系统概览] as SystemOverview
  [收入统计] as IncomeStats
}

package "首页模块" as HomeModule {
  [首页展示] as HomePage
  [热门课程] as HotCourses
  [最新课程] as NewCourses
  [分类导航] as CategoryNav
  [搜索功能] as SearchFunction
}

' 模块间关系
UserModule --> CourseModule : 用户浏览课程
UserModule --> LearningModule : 用户学习课程
UserModule --> PurchaseModule : 用户购买课程
UserModule --> AdminModule : 管理员管理

TeacherModule --> CourseModule : 教师创建课程
TeacherModule --> AdminModule : 课程审核

CourseModule --> LearningModule : 课程学习
CourseModule --> PurchaseModule : 课程购买

LearningModule --> PurchaseModule : 学习权限验证

AdminModule --> UserModule : 用户管理
AdminModule --> CourseModule : 课程管理
AdminModule --> TeacherModule : 教师管理

HomeModule --> CourseModule : 课程展示
HomeModule --> UserModule : 用户入口

note right of UserModule
  **用户管理**
  - 支持三种角色：管理员、教师、学生
  - JWT身份认证
  - 个人信息管理
end note

note right of TeacherModule
  **教师创作**
  - 课程全生命周期管理
  - 章节课时管理
  - 课程发布审核
end note

note right of LearningModule
  **学习功能**
  - 多媒体内容支持
  - 学习进度跟踪
  - 测验系统
end note

note right of PurchaseModule
  **购买系统**
  - 模拟充值功能
  - 课程购买流程
  - 余额管理
end note

note right of AdminModule
  **管理后台**
  - 课程审核管理
  - 用户权限管理
  - 数据统计分析
end note

@enduml
